Class TagSuggestion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.tag.TagSuggestion

  • public class TagSuggestion
extends Object
    TagSuggestion are suggested tags from a foreign system or within Communote. These suggestions can be used as tags.

    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
